ildren":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2178416778","tinyui":"/x/igDYgQ","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2178416778","webui":"/spaces/BAN/overview","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2178416778"}},{"id":"2259944189","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2259944189","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjI1OTk0NDE4OQ==","status":"current","title":"Documentación Técnica","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":44304616},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2259944189/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2259944189/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2259944189/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2259944189/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2259944189","tinyui":"/x/-QK0hg","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2259944189","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2259944189/Documentaci+n+T+cnica","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2259944189"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<h1>Breve overview de proceso 3DS</h1><ac:adf-extension><ac:adf-node type=\"panel\"><ac:adf-attribute key=\"panel-type\">note</ac:adf-attribute><ac:adf-content><p>Resumen hecho con IA</p></ac:adf-content></ac:adf-node><ac:adf-fallback><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" style=\"background-color: rgb(234,230,255);border-color: rgb(153,141,217);border-width: 1.0px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: rgb(234,230,255);\">\n<p>Resumen hecho con IA</p>\n</div></div></ac:adf-fallback></ac:adf-extension><p>El objetivo principal de 3D Secure es reducir el fraude en transacciones de e-commerce con tarjeta de cr&eacute;dito/d&eacute;bito, transfiriendo la responsabilidad del riesgo de fraude del comercio al emisor de la tarjeta.</p><p>El proceso se puede dividir en las siguientes etapas, que a menudo se entrelazan:</p><ol start=\"1\"><li><p><strong>Device Data Collection (DDC):</strong> El comprador entra en la p&aacute;gina de pago. Se carga un iframe oculto de Cardinal para recoger datos del dispositivo. Esta informaci&oacute;n incluye, entre otras cosas, el tipo de navegador, la resoluci&oacute;n de la pantalla, la direcci&oacute;n IP, y detalles del sistema operativo. Se obtiene como resultado un <code>SessionId</code></p></li><li><p><strong>Lookup:</strong> El comercio env&iacute;a una solicitud a Cardinal con los datos de la transacci&oacute;n y el <code>SessionId</code> del DDC. Cardinal contacta al directorio de esquemas de tarjetas para encontrar el ACS del emisor (Visa, Mastercard). El <code>Lookup</code> es el paso que determina si la transacci&oacute;n debe ser autenticada y, si es as&iacute;, cu&aacute;l es el siguiente paso. El resultado de esta b&uacute;squeda es lo que define el flujo de la transacci&oacute;n.</p></li><li><p><strong>Authenticate (decisi&oacute;n):</strong></p><ul><li><p>Si la transacci&oacute;n es de <strong>bajo riesgo</strong>, el ACS del emisor responde con una autenticaci&oacute;n exitosa (flujo &quot;frictionless&quot;). El comercio procede con la autorizaci&oacute;n de la transacci&oacute;n.</p></li><li><p>Si la transacci&oacute;n es de <strong>alto riesgo</strong>, el ACS responde que se requiere un <code>Challenge</code>.</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Challenge (si es necesario):</strong> El comercio inicia el <code>Challenge</code>, redirigiendo al comprador a la p&aacute;gina del ACS para completar la verificaci&oacute;n adicional. Una vez completado, el comprador es redirigido de vuelta al comercio con el resultado de la autenticaci&oacute;n.</p></li><li><p><strong>Autorizaci&oacute;n:</strong> El comercio, con el resultado exitoso de la autenticaci&oacute;n 3D Secure, procede a enviar la solicitud de autorizaci&oacute;n al procesador de pagos. Esta informaci&oacute;n de autenticaci&oacute;n es enviada en la solicitud de autorizaci&oacute;n, lo que transfiere la responsabilidad de fraude al emisor de la tarjeta.</p></li></ol><h1>Referencias</h1><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://app.diagrams.net/#G1YniFU4FFpyAKf6b983OaeJpLB7NblfRz#%7B%22pageId%22%3A%22Q6Qj3vK8hR4XFauKPOTc%22%7D\">https://app.diagrams.net/#G1YniFU4FFpyAKf6b983OaeJpLB7NblfRz#{&quot;pageId&quot;%3A&quot;Q6Qj3vK8hR4XFauKPOTc&quot;}</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://bancard.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/PRY/pages/1301741979/Servicios+transaccionales\" data-card-appearance=\"inline\">https://bancard.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/PRY/pages/1301741979/Servicios+transaccionales</a> </p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://bancard.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/P3ds2/pages/138838139/Servicios+jpos\" data-card-appearance=\"inline\">https://bancard.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/P3ds2/pages/138838139/Servicios+jpos</a>  </p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://bancard.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/TB/pages/1112506382/3DS+-+Tarjetas+de+pruebas\" data-card-appearance=\"inline\">https://bancard.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/TB/pages/1112506382/3DS+-+Tarjetas+de+pruebas</a>  </p></li></ul><p />","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/4021977089"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":980479836},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/4021977089/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/4021977089/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/4021977089/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/4021977089/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=4021977089","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/4021977089/Cardinal+3D+Secure","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/4021977089","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/4021977089","tinyui":"/x/AYC67w","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}